    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A strong woven fabric tape made in a herringbone twill weave that is used most often as button or seam reinforcement in the construction of garments, though other uses may include binding edges or as ties or closures. It may be made from a variety of natural and artificial fibers.</Note_Text>
